description: Have Alexa join you at the piano and have her coach you about the keys.  Just ask her a key, like "D minor", and she will tell the details of the key signature (the accidentals) and the relative key.  A great practice companion.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask relative keys to give me information on c major
Alexa ask relative keys to tell me about c minor
name: Relative Keys
shortDescription: Say a musical key and Alexa will tell you key signature and relative key.
